\title{Polynomial functors and cofunctors}
\taxon{reference}
\date{2022}
\meta{author}{David I. Spivak, Nelson Niu}

\p{D. I. Spivak and N. Niu. \em{Polynomial Functors: A Mathematical Theory of Interaction}. 2022. Defines cofunctors (comonoid maps in the category Poly) as the mathematical model of control. Used in the BCI pipeline ([[bci-0003]]) for the closed-loop cofunctor #{\mathrm{Brain} \to \mathrm{Decoder} \to \mathrm{Effector} \to \mathrm{Stimulator} \to \mathrm{Brain}}.}
